獨立調查委員會；<br />\n堅持一國兩制，反對港獨；<br />\n不認同破壞，不同意衝擊法院和醫院；更珍惜人和命，反對用任何力使人受傷。同意不分化，各自為香港努力。"},{"pid":"93d94257f579b08f07025f26e6e9adcb1b8d417a","tid":1625004,"uid":311714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5d428747bd83202e42dd0a949e7467cd0c7a4c69","tid":1625004,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"d6d4507e9b66d5b9b824f302e36126c8fddee183","tid":1625004,"uid":247840,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"紅色資本就係對準政權，即係共產黨<br />\n<br />\n你個共諜可以收收皮先"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:38:15.000Z","msg":"場運動幾時變左推翻中共？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果唔肯或唔敢承認對準政權唔係對準中共的話<br />\nChing你認真考慮吓出嚟抗爭嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n溫提：不推文回覆"},{"pid":"ea68d65942ce52f68f8f2dfc8fdb8218bebf0817","tid":1625004,"uid":138092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"你唯一未提嘅就係建制派辦事處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次有班人極力推蒙面法，係咩人？點解佢哋下下可以全身而退？<br />\n<br />\n就係因為焦點去咗第度。"},{"pid":"1e7b6e11a747727e3cb69b4fd147a45e3cf773e8","tid":1625004,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93d94257f579b08f07025f26e6e9adcb1b8d417a","tid":1625004,"uid":311714,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5d428747bd83202e42dd0a949e7467cd0c7a4c69","tid":1625004,"uid":8054,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"d6d4507e9b66d5b9b824f302e36126c8fddee183","tid":1625004,"uid":247840,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:36:54.000Z","msg":"紅色資本就係對準政權，即係共產黨<br />\n<br />\n你個共諜可以收收皮先"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:38:15.000Z","msg":"場運動幾時變左推翻中共？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"如果唔